    <div class="col-12 col-lg-9">
        <h3 class=" pink-text">Michel Grunberg</h3>
        <h4 class=" grey-text">Brand Advisor</h4>
        <p>Michel Grunberg has 37 years of global business and work experience in thr retail and beauty industries, 28 of which were with Estee Lauder Companies in senior capacities worldwide, in Europe-Middle East-Africa and most recently in the Asia-Pacific Region, including Singapore and China. He last served as Senior Vice President/Head of Asia-Pacific Region, having established the company’s fully-owned affiliate in China in 2001. He relocated to Shanghai in 2003 and retired from the Estee Lauder Group in April 2007.</p>
        <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="team-read-more pink-text" >Read More</a>
        <div class="team-more-bio" >
            <p>Based in Singapore and Sydney, he currently owns a consultancy company and is a director in Singapore on the Boards of C.K. Tang Limited (owner of Tangs Department Stores) and Parkson Retail Asia Limited (owner of Parkson and Centro department stores in Malaysia, Vietnam and Indonesia). He hold a BA and MBA in Business Administration and has lived and/or worked in diverse countries such as Turkey, Germany, France, England, Puerto Rico, Singapore, China and Australia.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
